The AP Ratios are so weak that it doesn't matter. Janna's AD ratio is 10%.  Raka's self heal is 40%. It doesn't even make sense to bother building that much AP. This is why Riot makes support items, 

Janna build:{{item:3504}} {{item:3069}} {{item:3165}} {{item:3117}} {{item:2049}}  {{item:3190}} 

Does it have AP? Yeah. Is it designed to make you kill/harass things? nope. Most of the items are cheap and high utility. You could even leave {{item:3105}} of the legion as is, really.
